text: The Torneig Internacional Els Gorchs is a tournament for professional female tennis players played on outdoor hard courts. The event is classified as a $60,000 ITF Women's Circuit tournament and has been held in Les Franqueses del Vallès, Spain, since 2005. == Past finals == === Singles === {|class="wikitable"
